<section
  class="md:px-12 sm:px-8 relative border-b border-zinc-700 scroll-mt-24 2xl:border-x"
>
  <div class="border-x border-zinc-700 divide-zinc-700">
    <div
      class="divide-y divide-zinc-700 "
    >
      <div class="p-8 lg:px-20">
        <span class="text-cyan-400"> Customers love it</span><h2
          class="lg:text-2xl py-3 tracking-tight font-light max-w-xl text-white"
        >
          Hired by design agencies, creators, freelances, universities, and
          numerous individuals representing companies across diverse industries
          worldwide.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:items-center lg:divide-x divide-zinc-700"
        x-data="{ testimonialActive: 2 }"
      >
        <div class="p-8 lg:px-20 shrink-0">
          <button
            @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 1"
            class="inline-block mx-2 font-bold rounded-full shadow-xs focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 h-12 w-12 opacity-25 ring-1 ring-offset-4 ring-zinc-700 ring-offset-black bg-gradientdown"
            :class="{'h-12 w-12 opacity-25 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive != 1, 'opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white': testimonialActive == 1 }"
            ><img
              class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full grayscale"
              src="/tonylea.jpg"
              alt="#"
            /></button
          ><button
            @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 2"
            class="inline-block mx-2 font-bold rounded-full shadow-xs focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 ring-1 ring-offset-4 ring-zinc-700 ring-offset-black opacity-100 bg-gradientdown"
            :class="{'h-12 w-12 opacity-25 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive != 2, 'opacity-100 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive == 2 }"
            ><img
              class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full grayscale"
              src="/robaustin.jpg"
              alt="Rob ustin"
            /></button
          ><button
            @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 3"
            class="inline-block mx-2 font-bold rounded-full shadow-xs focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 h-12 w-12 opacity-25 ring-1 ring-offset-4 ring-zinc-700 ring-offset-black bg-gradientdown"
            :class="{'h-12 w-12 opacity-25 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive != 3, 'opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white': testimonialActive == 3 }"
            ><img
              class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full grayscale"
              src="/volkan.jpg"
              alt="@heychazza on twitter"
            /></button
          >
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 lg:px-20 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start gap-12">
          <div class="flex">
            <div
              class=""
              x-show="testimonialActive == 1"
              style="display: none;"
            >
              <h2 class="text-zinc-400 text-sm font-mediumlgext-base">
                Tony Lea
              </h2><a href="#" class="text-xs text-zinc-400"
                >Founder of DevDojo</a
              >
            </div><div class="" x-show="testimonialActive == 2">
              <h2 class="text-white text-sm font-mediumlgext-base">
                Robert Austin
              </h2><a href="#" class="text-xs text-zinc-400"
                >Founder of Built At Lightspeed.</a
              >
            </div><div
              class=""
              x-show="testimonialActive == 3"
              style="display: none;"
            >
              <h2 class="text-white text-sm font-mediumlgext-base">
                Volkan Kaja
              </h2><a href="#" class="text-xs text-zinc-400">
                Founder of Versoly</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div
              x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 1"
              style="display: none;"
            >
              <p
                class="text-zinc-300 text-base max-w-xl"
                x-show.transition="testimonialActive == 1"
                style="display: none;"
              >
                Michael is a true rarity, effortlessly bridging the realms of
                design and coding. His designs are masterfully polished,
                striking a perfect balance between being on trend and remaining
                distincltly original.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 2">
              <p
                class="text-zinc-300 text-base max-w-xl"
                x-show.transition="testimonialActive == 2"
              >
                Michael has a great eye for design and he is an absolute
                pleasure to work with. I definitely plan on working with him on
                future projects of mine. I wholeheartedly recommend him to
                anyone seeking standout, quality work.
              </p>
            </div><div
              x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 3"
              style="display: none;"
            >
              <p
                class="text-zinc-300 text-base max-w-xl"
                x-show.transition="testimonialActive == 3"
                style="display: none;"
              >
                Michael is a rare breed of designer & dev that understands
                business needs. He leveraged his previous experience to build
                out a few landings very quickly for Versoly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
